lambda operator or lambda function

it creates small anonymous functions. these functions are throw-away functions 
lambda function is used with:
	filter()
	map()
	reduce()

I cannot use lambda with if

syntax of lambda

	lambda argument_list: expression 

#######map()#######

function that takes two arguments

map(func, seq)

func	mane of the function
seq	sequence 

map applies the functions func to all elements of the sequence seq
it returns a new list of elements  

##map() used with lambda##

syntax
	map(lambda argument_list: expression, list)

map() can be applied to more than one list
lists must have the same lenght


#######filter()#######
it filter out all the element of a list and return the element that verify the fcuntion (that have True)

syntax 
	filter(function, list)
